snippet.title: Ruby: Huntress of Vale Combat
snippet.description:
Trying out something to simulate camera shake when getting hit and certain attacks. As well as simple parallax scrolling for my #RWBY Fangame. What do you think?

Coming soon to "Ruby: Huntress of Vale"!

Interested in the game? You can get it on Itch and Gamejolt!
